description: Lohilo Foods AB engages in the production of ice cream and other confectionery products. The company is headquartered in Vaxjo, Kronoberg. The company went IPO on 2020-10-26. The firm produces ice cream, as well as functional food and functional drinks but also protein bars, chewing gum and chips. The products in the Company’s portfolio include product portfolio include LOHILO, Alvestaglass, Haagen-Dazs, NICK's, Bubbies and Jarnaglass.
name: Lohilo Foods AB (publ)
